{
  "stem": "18281.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 405.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we have the parlor where the piano was and the merchandise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Class It was quite a large apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my dad was an aficionado of, of classical music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while my mother also liked music, she didn't know as much about, about the classics than my dad did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was playing the piano.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for my dad's birthday, she would surprise him with a new air that she had practiced in secret.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was his birthday present, that she could play another song or another air.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did have a seat at the opera for a certain time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the end, I don't think we had it anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yes, I do remember-- probably I was 10, 11-- when my first opera was I went to the theater and saw some German pieces and, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't Shakespeare for sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think it was Kleist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was not, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came from a family that was absolutely not religious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, my mother's family was not religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, when I went to school, you had to identify yourself as a Israelite.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In those days, we weren't called Jews were called-- the religion Israelitish, which is Israelite.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go to a, a cheder, religious school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember very small kind of room where we had lessons, Hebrew lessons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also, that's where I learnt my-- to study for my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I made my bar mitzvah in, in December probably of-- oh, it probably was the-- February, 1938.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the last time our family was together, all, all the different branches of our family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because in March, 1938, the, the Germans marched in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had the familiar, famous Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
